=== Example 002: Basic printf command ===
Using system() to call printf:
Hello, World!

printf with multiple format specifiers:
Name: Alice, Age: 25, Score: 95.50

printf with different format types:
Integer: 42
Float: 3.14
String: test
Character: 6
Hexadecimal: ff
Octal: 100

printf with field width and padding:
Item1        100
Item2       2000
Item3         30

printf with precision:
3.142
1.23e+06

printf with zero padding:
00042
000000ff

printf with Perl variables:
Variable: Perl, Count: 42
